{"tid":1701192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"老實講如果1111重係玩玩下 我諗好多本身會罷嘅人都心鳩淡","createTime":"2019-11-09T02:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:20:41.000Z","uid":33775,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7e391b0e91d9c81034f9fc3738c86bbc7b8b96","tid":1701192,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"我就係其中一個<br />\n我基本上每一次有人叫罷我就罷<br />\n但我唯一覺得有少少意義就係得85 （機場還眼唔知叫唔叫罷工）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後102我以為健仔一槍會叫醒大家<br />\n但我睇到嘅只係五區集合點 得十幾條友都冇<br />\n最後咩都搞唔成 係商場禁飛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有睇到成班工照返 之後搞咩快閃lunchtime嘅人<br />\n其實對公司根本harmless 睇到心鳩淡<br />\n重有太多零散嘅罷工 我都已經唔記得日期 因為根本咩行動都冇<br />\n<br />\n重有fd話你on9咁都信 最後得我同2個fd去集合點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n1. 出到黎都見到有好多灰撚左嘅手足<br />\n2. 罷工都要犧牲架 你玩多兩次真係冇人再同你玩<br />\n3. 如果淨罷一日 同放al冇分別<br />\n4. 2日都好 你地可唔可以返少2日工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.<span style=\"color: red;\"> 罷工明明係和理非大主線活動 和理非自己唔郁 要勇武幫埋你塞路爆鐵 之後講到好慘咁好想返但冇車先唔返 咁叫和勇不分咩 而家係人地做埋你果份 人地都未撚割你 你有咩資格割人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca9a086326914f044819a1a64cb26e404f7b333","tid":1701192,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"早晨 <br />\n記得出門前 上 twitter retweet<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\n（最新!!）Senator Rubio講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=4965c013\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&h=370276c8\" data-auto-link target=\"